學之後肯拎起本書認真一課一課咁讀<br />\n呢個係最快最好既方法 但亦係好少人做得到"},{"pid":"df4cf45b6700d1397450aa52ad542d535f7cea39","tid":2073453,"uid":99086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1853d6ddfc6ede76742139aa16ba7f29d1de711c","tid":2073453,"uid":350842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e920347e9aaf124fb777d8ed994d8c454e717471","tid":2073453,"uid":99086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"896845588fc69b9c2f003d232f23b6273dc4202c","tid":2073453,"uid":145928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T17:44:02.000Z","msg":"上堂嘅考過左n4 就自學啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：n4 考過左1年後考n2 仲要last 一個月先睇past paper"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T00:36:16.000Z","msg":"N4同N2差幾遠？<br />\n跟老師學緊n4野 想出年7月直接考n3/n2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T19:31:55.000Z","msg":"N4應該係N2既20%進度左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你只求合格既話 香港人應該一年由n5衝n2唔大問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好像似我呢種文科廢J都做到"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:48:06.000Z","msg":"求住合格先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />得一年都唔敢aim太高"},{"pid":"6bec62b662ff524dc5405bedbbeaa79c3756379e","tid":2073453,"uid":350842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df4cf45b6700d1397450aa52ad542d535f7cea39","tid":2073453,"uid":99086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1853d6ddfc6ede76742139aa16ba7f29d1de711c","tid":2073453,"uid":350842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e920347e9aaf124fb777d8ed994d8c454e717471","tid":2073453,"uid":99086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T00:36:16.000Z","msg":"N4同N2差幾遠？<br />\n跟老師學緊n4野 想出年7月直接考n3/n2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T19:31:55.000Z","msg":"N4應該係N2既20%進度左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你只求合格既話 香港人應該一年由n5衝n2唔大問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好像似我呢種文科廢J都做到"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T11:48:06.000Z","msg":"求住合格先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />得一年都唔敢aim太高"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T12:04:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人幾有優勢 係學日文上面 首先識唔少英文<br />\n又寫繁體 基本上係解決左睇漢字同睇片仮名既問題　(読解力)<br />\n不過淨係見字解義係唔夠 仲要知點讀 因為有言語知識部份<br />\n<br />\n關於文法有啲Basic rule同priority  <br />\n黎黎去去係 形 名 助 動詞  分清詞性 基本上拆句就好簡單<br />\n~ものを~ / ~もの・を~ 前者固定句 (助詞) 後者 名詞加助詞<br />\n例如_ない &larr; い形容詞<br />\n<br />\n香港人天生比人培訓成考試機器 呢啲技巧野應該唔係咩大問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n比較重要一點係助詞可以睇下youtube日本人點教 (助詞一開始唔明其實都冇咩所謂 都係啲經驗野黎)<br />\n因為有啲本地老師講到好學術 又咩歸著點 接觸點  <br />\n講到尾 其實都係一個概念與其見到個字就拎張LIST出黎查下係咪 歸著點 接觸點<br />\n不如親身體驗下日本人思維 咁樣學得有樂趣啲"},{"pid":"78c4da849850a77c129bddb6b78d870619dffd81","tid":2073453,"uid":73464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T12:32:17.000Z","msg":"依家喺日本，唔學唔得🤪"},{"pid":"9ce1565824da4b6bf32eb820b4085a5677e740eb","tid":2073453,"uid":1089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T13:36:50.000Z","msg":"我個方法就奇怪啲<br />\n搵左其中一段JR既車內自動放送黎背到入腦(特急はるか)<br />\n佢讀音一定最準確同埋通常都混合左幾個助詞運用，同埋會有埋尊敬語<br />\n車掌講野就當練聽解<br />\n<br />\n利申 日本鐵膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab4433aad105fb51a76811a0610087ab4cd56eb","tid":2073453,"uid":66734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:49:41.000Z","msg":"自學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n舊年直接考n2 150/180 可能年尾或者出年考埋n1<br />\n不過我其實冇乜特別去學或者溫書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淨係平時成日睇日劇綜藝之類 同埋有like啲日文page間唔中睇下 仲有舊年開始會上twitter同日本人傾下計"},{"pid":"e4da88ccd35b58289fc3344c3bb9824029394997","tid":2073453,"u